==============
screen-watcher
==============
screen-watcher is a utility for watching terminating processes.

============
Installation
============
::

    pip install screen-watcher

=====
Usage
=====
::

    SLACK_BOT_TOKEN=token SLACK_BOT_CHANNEL=screen-watcher screen-watcher --daemon

